Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.68,0:00:03.46,Main Dialogue,Honoka,0000,0000,0000,,Hishiron! Let's get lunch.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.08,0:00:09.94,Main Dialogue,Hishiro,0000,0000,0000,,What about Kariu-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.42,0:00:13.68,Main Dialogue,Honoka,0000,0000,0000,,C-Come on, Hishiron!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.68,0:00:15.93,Main Dialogue,Honoka,0000,0000,0000,,It's lunch break.\NHow haven't you noticed yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.93,0:00:17.65,Main Dialogue,Honoka,0000,0000,0000,,Rena's absent today.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.60,0:00:22.11,Main Dialogue,Hishiro,0000,0000,0000,,She is? Then it's just the two of us today.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.96,0:00:24.81,Main Dialogue,Honoka,0000,0000,0000,,Yep!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.05,0:02:01.64,Episode Title,,0000,0000,0000,,Revenge
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.39,0:02:06.42,Main Dialogue,Honoka,0000,0000,0000,,Hishiron, ramen again?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.42,0:02:08.05,Main Dialogue,Honoka,0000,0000,0000,,There's other good stuff\N on the menu here.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.05,0:02:10.50,Main Dialogue,Honoka,0000,0000,0000,,Like the fried rice and the rice omelets...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.26,0:02:14.47,Main Dialogue,Hishiro,0000,0000,0000,,Tamarai-san, you look a little ugly today.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.89,0:02:17.95,Main Dialogue,Hishiro,0000,0000,0000,,Your eyes look weird.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.95,0:02:20.15,Main Dialogue,Hishiro,0000,0000,0000,,Did you walk into something?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.15,0:02:23.03,Main Dialogue,Honoka,0000,0000,0000,,Stop, Hishiron! Don't be mean!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.03,0:02:25.25,Main Dialogue,Honoka,0000,0000,0000,,"Ugly"? "Weird"?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.45,0:02:30.48,Italics Dialogue,Honoka,0000,0000,0000,,It's that obvious I was crying, huh? Ugh...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.48,0:02:32.86,Main Dialogue,Hishiro,0000,0000,0000,,If you didn't bump into anything,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.23,0:02:35.26,Main Dialogue,Hishiro,0000,0000,0000,,was it bees?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.57,0:02:38.30,Main Dialogue,Honoka,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.30,0:02:40.75,Main Dialogue,Honoka,0000,0000,0000,,Guess I was stung in my sleep!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.87,0:02:44.08,Main Dialogue,Hishiro,0000,0000,0000,,I see. Get well soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.11,0:02:54.61,Main Dialogue,Honoka,0000,0000,0000,,Say, Hishiron...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.89,0:03:02.88,Main Dialogue,Honoka,0000,0000,0000,,Have you ever hurt someone or clashed\Nwith them because you're too smart?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.51,0:03:05.63,Main Dialogue,Honoka,0000,0000,0000,,Made people give up,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.63,0:03:08.34,Main Dialogue,Honoka,0000,0000,0000,,or tell you to do everything by yourself?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.64,0:03:10.86,Main Dialogue,Honoka,0000,0000,0000,,Anything like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.25,0:03:16.15,Main Dialogue,Hishiro,0000,0000,0000,,I don't really understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.13,0:03:19.12,Main Dialogue,Honoka,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, weird question.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.12,0:03:20.43,Main Dialogue,Honoka,0000,0000,0000,,Forget it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.89,0:03:29.01,Main Dialogue,Rena,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.31,0:03:30.31,Main Dialogue,Amatsu,0000,0000,0000,,Rena!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.32,0:03:32.05,Main Dialogue,Amatsu,0000,0000,0000,,How's your ankle?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.05,0:03:35.19,Main Dialogue,Amatsu,0000,0000,0000,,You went to the hospital, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.53,0:03:46.45,Flashback Dialogue,Team,0000,0000,0000,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.25,0:03:48.43,Flashback Dialogue,Team,0000,0000,0000,,Nice spike!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.07,0:03:51.50,Flashback Dialogue,Rena,0000,0000,0000,,One more!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.50,0:03:52.00,Flashback Dialogue,Team,0000,0000,0000,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.46,0:03:55.68,Flashback Dialogue,Team,0000,0000,0000,,Tamarai-senpai!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.75,0:04:05.01,Flashback Dialogue,Amatsu,0000,0000,0000,,Get the nurse!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.46,0:04:10.69,Main Dialogue,Rena,0000,0000,0000,,It's a sprain.\NIt'll take two weeks to heal.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.69,0:04:12.73,Main Dialogue,Rena,0000,0000,0000,,I can exercise after that,\Nbut with caution.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.74,0:04:14.23,Main Dialogue,Amatsu,0000,0000,0000,,Whew.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.23,0:04:16.24,Main Dialogue,Amatsu,0000,0000,0000,,Then you can make the tournament!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.24,0:04:20.11,Main Dialogue,Amatsu,0000,0000,0000,,You can come by practice until it heals.\NJust to show your face.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.11,0:04:22.39,Main Dialogue,Amatsu,0000,0000,0000,,They'll all be relieved.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.39,0:04:23.94,Main Dialogue,Rena,0000,0000,0000,,About that...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.08,0:04:30.29,Main Dialogue,Rena,0000,0000,0000,,I think I'd drag the team down if I played\Nin a match after taking two weeks off.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.29,0:04:32.09,Main Dialogue,Rena,0000,0000,0000,,And I don't know if\NI'll be able to move right.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.41,0:04:34.55,Main Dialogue,Rena,0000,0000,0000,,I think I'm just gonna retire.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.85,0:04:37.73,Main Dialogue,Rena,0000,0000,0000,,Let the others know for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.73,0:04:38.46,Main Dialogue,Rena,0000,0000,0000,,Bye.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.19,0:04:41.80,Main Dialogue,Amatsu,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, Rena!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.65,0:04:50.83,Main Dialogue,Honoka,0000,0000,0000,,You should try the rice omelet next time!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.05,0:04:52.12,Main Dialogue,Hishiro,0000,0000,0000,,Kariu-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.55,0:05:09.55,Main Dialogue,Honoka,0000,0000,0000,,I've gotta use the bathroom.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.55,0:05:10.12,Main Dialogue,Hishiro,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.29,0:05:31.11,Main Dialogue,Honoka,0000,0000,0000,,R...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.02,0:05:55.79,Main Dialogue,Asaji,0000,0000,0000,,No, Aki, stop.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.00,0:05:58.81,Main Dialogue,Asaji,0000,0000,0000,,What were you gonna do?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.81,0:06:01.53,Main Dialogue,Inukai,0000,0000,0000,,Drag her in front of Tama \Nand make her apologize.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.53,0:06:02.71,Main Dialogue,Asaji,0000,0000,0000,,You can't!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.61,0:06:05.66,Main Dialogue,Asaji,0000,0000,0000,,You heard what Tama-chan said.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.66,0:06:07.97,Main Dialogue,Asaji,0000,0000,0000,,She wants to stay friends with Kariu-san,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.97,0:06:09.68,Main Dialogue,Asaji,0000,0000,0000,,so she'll figure this out herself.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.16,0:06:11.75,Main Dialogue,Asaji,0000,0000,0000,,Watch over her.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.75,0:06:13.72,Main Dialogue,Inukai,0000,0000,0000,,I've been doing that {\i1}all day.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.72,0:06:15.12,Main Dialogue,Inukai,0000,0000,0000,,Show more patience.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.81,0:06:19.36,Main Dialogue,Inukai,0000,0000,0000,,She was finally smiling at practice.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.36,0:06:21.93,Main Dialogue,Inukai,0000,0000,0000,,Now it's making her cry again.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.93,0:06:23.13,Main Dialogue,Inukai,0000,0000,0000,,It's hard for me to watch.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.91,0:06:27.38,Main Dialogue,Oga,0000,0000,0000,,Kariu, are you not going to practice?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.38,0:06:29.73,Main Dialogue,Rena,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna study a bit today.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.29,0:06:35.99,Main Dialogue,Oga,0000,0000,0000,,Then since I'm not working today, maybe I\Nshould do my homework before I go home.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.39,0:06:39.02,Main Dialogue,Oga,0000,0000,0000,,Arata, you're staying, right?\NFor make-up prep?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.02,0:06:42.05,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, I've got somewhere to be today.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.32,0:06:43.60,Main Dialogue,Oga,0000,0000,0000,,Dude, what?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.60,0:06:45.96,Main Dialogue,Oga,0000,0000,0000,,At this rate, you'll fail next week, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.96,0:06:47.04,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.65,0:06:48.34,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,Bye.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.95,0:06:56.67,Italics Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,I'm being a nosy old man and \Nleaving you two alone together.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.67,0:06:59.10,Italics Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,Be grateful and enjoy your youth.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.41,0:07:09.58,Italics Dialogue,Rena,0000,0000,0000,,How long is he gonna stay?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.39,0:07:12.70,Italics Dialogue,Rena,0000,0000,0000,,I was just waiting for everyone to leave...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.09,0:07:16.15,Italics Dialogue,Rena,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want to be seen \Ndragging my foot like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.41,0:07:21.02,Main Dialogue,Rena,0000,0000,0000,,Okay! Guess I'd better be go—
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.02,0:07:22.60,Main Dialogue,Oga,0000,0000,0000,,Okay! All done!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.53,0:07:26.23,Main Dialogue,Oga,0000,0000,0000,,You finished, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.23,0:07:28.05,Main Dialogue,Oga,0000,0000,0000,,Then let's go home together!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.05,0:07:30.33,Italics Dialogue,Rena,0000,0000,0000,,His timing is the worst!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.87,0:07:33.30,Main Dialogue,Rena,0000,0000,0000,,You go on ahead, Oga.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.30,0:07:36.25,Main Dialogue,Oga,0000,0000,0000,,Why? Aren't you done, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.25,0:07:37.11,Main Dialogue,Rena,0000,0000,0000,,Just go.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.11,0:07:38.39,Main Dialogue,Oga,0000,0000,0000,,You're not making any sense.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.39,0:07:39.23,Main Dialogue,Rena,0000,0000,0000,,Just go!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.23,0:07:41.23,Main Dialogue,Rena,0000,0000,0000,,Don't try to make sense of it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.23,0:07:42.47,Main Dialogue,Rena,0000,0000,0000,,Take a hint already!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.95,0:07:48.09,Main Dialogue,Oga,0000,0000,0000,,What? Man, you're extra grumpy today.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.09,0:07:49.95,Main Dialogue,Rena,0000,0000,0000,,Don't talk like I'm always grumpy!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.95,0:07:52.91,Main Dialogue,Oga,0000,0000,0000,,Come on. Stop sulking, and let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.91,0:07:55.41,Main Dialogue,Rena,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Stop that, you wimpy...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.93,0:08:01.60,Main Dialogue,Oga,0000,0000,0000,,Kariu!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.60,0:08:02.55,Main Dialogue,Oga,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, are—
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.60,0:08:02.55,Main Dialogue Top,Oga,0000,0000,0000,,Don't look!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.55,0:08:03.94,Main Dialogue,Oga,0000,0000,0000,,Ow...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.94,0:08:05.05,Main Dialogue,Rena,0000,0000,0000,,Just leave me alone!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.05,0:08:06.06,Main Dialogue,Oga,0000,0000,0000,,Why, you...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.89,0:08:12.81,Main Dialogue,Rena,0000,0000,0000,,Didn't you hear me?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.81,0:08:14.79,Main Dialogue,Rena,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you still here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.79,0:08:16.67,Main Dialogue,Rena,0000,0000,0000,,Just leave already!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.05,0:08:22.15,Main Dialogue,Oga,0000,0000,0000,,I can't just leave a crying\Ngirl alone and go home.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.93,0:08:25.32,Main Dialogue,Oga,0000,0000,0000,,I'm too wimpy to carry you,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.32,0:08:26.79,Main Dialogue,Oga,0000,0000,0000,,but I can lend you a shoulder,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.79,0:08:28.63,Main Dialogue,Oga,0000,0000,0000,,and get you down the stairs.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.71,0:08:33.04,Main Dialogue,Oga,0000,0000,0000,,The last thing you need is a fall.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.71,0:08:59.30,Italics Dialogue,Rena,0000,0000,0000,,If I were a boy,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.68,0:09:01.93,Italics Dialogue,Rena,0000,0000,0000,,I'd hate girls like me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.93,0:09:06.29,Italics Dialogue,Rena,0000,0000,0000,,Stupidly proud, short-tempered,\Nand utterly incomprehensible.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.57,0:09:12.77,Italics Dialogue,Rena,0000,0000,0000,,I was so mean to Honoka.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.17,0:09:15.41,Italics Dialogue,Rena,0000,0000,0000,,She might never speak to me again.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.13,0:09:22.79,Italics Dialogue,Rena,0000,0000,0000,,But I can't be honest\Nabout my feelings.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.23,0:09:25.82,Italics Dialogue,Rena,0000,0000,0000,,I'm really starting to hate myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.85,0:09:35.93,Main Dialogue,An,0000,0000,0000,,Man, I just don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.93,0:09:37.10,Italics Dialogue,Ryo,0000,0000,0000,,About what?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.10,0:09:40.68,Main Dialogue,An,0000,0000,0000,,There's just so much happening \Nthat the subject doesn't see.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.05,0:09:44.16,Main Dialogue,An,0000,0000,0000,,Even though one of the goals of ReLIFE
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.16,0:09:47.27,Main Dialogue,An,0000,0000,0000,,is to reinvigorate emotions \Nthat have withered with age
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.27,0:09:48.19,Main Dialogue,An,0000,0000,0000,,by getting him involved \Nwith adolescent kids.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.19,0:09:49.81,Italics Dialogue,An,0000,0000,0000,,by getting him involved \Nwith adolescent kids.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.77,0:09:53.17,Italics Dialogue,An,0000,0000,0000,,Will he actually get involved?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.87,0:09:58.20,Main Dialogue,Ryo,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I'm sure Kaizaki-san will notice\Nsomething's wrong soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.05,0:10:00.53,Main Dialogue,Ryo,0000,0000,0000,,But what then?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.02,0:10:30.65,sign_15058_137_friends_acting_w,,0000,0000,0000,,friends acting weird help
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.90,0:10:34.65,Italics Dialogue,Hishiro,0000,0000,0000,,I knew it. Something's wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.28,0:10:39.45,Italics Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,Weird...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.82,0:10:41.95,Italics Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,What's been going on lately?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.49,0:10:46.54,Italics Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,I thought Hishiro-san and Kariu \Nhad finally became friends,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.54,0:10:50.75,Italics Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,but now even Tamarai-san's\Neating lunch alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.08,0:10:54.21,Italics Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,Kariu hasn't been going to practice.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.21,0:10:56.38,Italics Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,Things don't seem right\N between her and Oga, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.76,0:11:00.13,Italics Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,What's with this awkward atmosphere?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.05,0:11:02.47,Italics Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.97,0:11:06.60,Flashback Italics Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,What's with this company?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.89,0:11:08.18,Flashback Italics Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,Something's off.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.64,0:11:11.60,Flashback Italics Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,Do my seniors hate each other?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.35,0:11:13.56,Flashback Dialogue,Sempai,0000,0000,0000,,Kaizaki-kun...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.90,0:11:18.61,Flashback Dialogue,Sempai,0000,0000,0000,,You're absolutely right, \Nand I'm glad you feel that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.86,0:11:21.86,Flashback Dialogue,Sempai,0000,0000,0000,,But I want you to stay out of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.87,0:11:29.50,sign_16493_153_Hishiro_Chizuru,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,1)}Hishiro Chizuru
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.16,0:11:29.50,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,It's Hishiro-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.50,0:11:33.00,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,Let's see..."I need your advice."
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.63,0:11:36.80,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,"I'm outside your place."
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.80,0:11:39.38,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,"Can we talk?"
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.26,0:11:43.14,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.68,0:11:44.64,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,No way! Why?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.97,0:11:50.43,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,Scary! Too scary!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.43,0:11:51.64,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.56,0:11:55.69,Main Dialogue,Hishiro,0000,0000,0000,,Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.52,0:11:57.90,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,What brings you here?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.90,0:12:00.57,Main Dialogue,Hishiro,0000,0000,0000,,Like I said, I need your help.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.57,0:12:03.45,Main Dialogue,Hishiro,0000,0000,0000,,Since it would be a little wordy for LIME,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.45,0:12:05.62,Main Dialogue,Hishiro,0000,0000,0000,,I figured in person was better.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.62,0:12:07.87,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,You could have just called.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.08,0:12:14.46,Main Dialogue,Hishiro,0000,0000,0000,,I've never had a long \Nphone call with a friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.46,0:12:16.54,Main Dialogue,Hishiro,0000,0000,0000,,It never even occurred to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.96,0:12:20.42,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,Well, uh, come on in.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.42,0:12:22.09,Main Dialogue,Hishiro,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.85,0:12:30.10,Main Dialogue,Hishiro,0000,0000,0000,,You live alone?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.10,0:12:31.93,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,Well, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.93,0:12:33.77,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, sit anywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.77,0:12:34.48,Main Dialogue,Hishiro,0000,0000,0000,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.85,0:12:35.72,Italics Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.02,0:12:37.69,Italics Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,She's in high school.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.69,0:12:41.74,Italics Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,Generally when you go to a friend's house, \Ntheir family's around.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.78,0:12:46.66,Italics Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, is Hishiro-san freaking out \Nbecause it's just me here?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.53,0:12:50.83,Italics Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,What now? Should I give her \Nan excuse to leave?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.83,0:12:53.66,Italics Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,No, she's Oga-level dense.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.66,0:12:55.50,Italics Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,I doubt she cares at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.46,0:12:58.96,Italics Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, I'm the one freaking out!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.96,0:13:00.71,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,U-Uh, here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.26,0:13:02.55,Main Dialogue,Hishiro,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.55,0:13:09.22,Main Dialogue,Hishiro,0000,0000,0000,,Go ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.22,0:13:10.85,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.52,0:13:13.98,Italics Dialogue,An,0000,0000,0000,,Don't jump her!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.98,0:13:19.06,Italics Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,How can I, with you guys watching?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.06,0:13:19.90,Italics Dialogue,An,0000,0000,0000,,Tee hee!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.61,0:13:22.78,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,So, what's up?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.78,0:13:25.78,Main Dialogue,Hishiro,0000,0000,0000,,It's about Kariu-san and Tamarai-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.07,0:13:27.57,Main Dialogue,Hishiro,0000,0000,0000,,It's weird.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.57,0:13:32.66,Main Dialogue,Hishiro,0000,0000,0000,,They were so close, and now \Nthey won't speak to each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.66,0:13:36.83,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,I was wondering if you knew what happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.58,0:13:41.92,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry. It's bugging me, too, but I dunno.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.92,0:13:43.46,Main Dialogue,Hishiro,0000,0000,0000,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.09,0:13:47.34,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,But I'm surprised you've been so perceptive.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.09,0:13:52.56,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,It wasn't long ago that you'd have \Nasked them directly.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.97,0:13:56.89,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,But you realized you couldn't, \Nso you came to see me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.56,0:13:59.27,Main Dialogue,Hishiro,0000,0000,0000,,That's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.90,0:14:02.94,Main Dialogue,Hishiro,0000,0000,0000,,Why did I go the long way around?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.73,0:14:06.99,Main Dialogue,Hishiro,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I think it's because\Nit isn't my problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.99,0:14:11.53,Main Dialogue,Hishiro,0000,0000,0000,,I'm emotionally dumb, \Nso I make a lot of mistakes.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.03,0:14:14.95,Main Dialogue,Hishiro,0000,0000,0000,,If it's just me, that's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.95,0:14:17.33,Main Dialogue,Hishiro,0000,0000,0000,,But with Kariu-san and Tamarai-san,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.33,0:14:20.75,Main Dialogue,Hishiro,0000,0000,0000,,I can't afford to be stupid and mess up.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.75,0:14:22.96,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,You don't need to be so hard on yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.34,0:14:28.80,Main Dialogue,Hishiro,0000,0000,0000,,Last year, there was bullying in my class.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.80,0:14:32.14,Italics Dialogue,Hishiro,0000,0000,0000,,It was not pleasant to see.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.14,0:14:34.31,Italics Dialogue,Hishiro,0000,0000,0000,,I had this weird sense of duty,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.68,0:14:38.69,Main Dialogue,Hishiro,0000,0000,0000,,like it was my job to stop it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.69,0:14:42.11,Main Dialogue,Hishiro,0000,0000,0000,,So I told them to stop this nonsense.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.40,0:14:45.73,Main Dialogue,Hishiro,0000,0000,0000,,The bullying just got worse.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.15,0:14:48.65,Main Dialogue,Hishiro,0000,0000,0000,,And the victim told me...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.03,0:14:51.07,Main Dialogue,Hishiro,0000,0000,0000,,"Don't do anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.07,0:14:55.91,Main Dialogue,Hishiro,0000,0000,0000,,All I have to do is put up with it,\N and it won't get any worse."
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.20,0:14:59.79,Flashback Dialogue,Sempai,0000,0000,0000,,You're absolutely right.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.79,0:15:03.13,Flashback Dialogue,Sempai,0000,0000,0000,,But in any society, \Nyou just need to grin and bear it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.13,0:15:04.92,Flashback Dialogue,Sempai,0000,0000,0000,,Even if it isn't fair.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.55,0:15:07.51,Flashback Dialogue,Sempai,0000,0000,0000,,I'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.67,0:15:11.30,Flashback Dialogue,Sempai,0000,0000,0000,,So, Kaizaki-kun... grow up.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.68,0:15:17.14,Main Dialogue,Hishiro,0000,0000,0000,,I think she was doing her best
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.14,0:15:19.77,Main Dialogue,Hishiro,0000,0000,0000,,to maintain the balance in her little world.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.77,0:15:23.86,Main Dialogue,Hishiro,0000,0000,0000,,But I stepped in, heeding only my emotions,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.86,0:15:26.23,Main Dialogue,Hishiro,0000,0000,0000,,and made things worse.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.23,0:15:27.90,Main Dialogue,Hishiro,0000,0000,0000,,I really regretted it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.90,0:15:33.28,Main Dialogue,Hishiro,0000,0000,0000,,I just don't know how to act while\Nconsidering other people's feelings.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.28,0:15:37.04,Main Dialogue,Hishiro,0000,0000,0000,,After that, I did what she said. \NI said nothing
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.04,0:15:39.16,Main Dialogue,Hishiro,0000,0000,0000,,and pretended I saw nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.21,0:15:43.28,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,What happened to her?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.21,0:15:46.96,Main Dialogue,Hishiro,0000,0000,0000,,She changed schools after the year ended.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.67,0:15:48.71,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.72,0:15:53.34,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,Something similar happened to me last year.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.05,0:15:58.97,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,At my last... school, \Na senpai was... bullied.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.64,0:16:03.23,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,I got all fired up and tried to help.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.81,0:16:06.65,Italics Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,I lashed out at the people bullying her.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.98,0:16:08.36,Italics Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,But like you said,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.78,0:16:12.61,Italics Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,Senpai was maintaining her own balance.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.36,0:16:15.53,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,And I upset that.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.08,0:16:18.66,Main Dialogue,Hishiro,0000,0000,0000,,And your senpai?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.33,0:16:21.44,Main Dialogue,Hishiro,0000,0000,0000,,What happened to her?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.75,0:16:26.96,Flashback Dialogue,Hishiro,0000,0000,0000,,And your senpai...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.59,0:16:28.84,Flashback Dialogue,Hishiro,0000,0000,0000,,...what happened...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.51,0:16:35.05,Flashback Dialogue,Hishiro,0000,0000,0000,,...to her?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.77,0:16:47.02,Main Dialogue,Hishiro,0000,0000,0000,,Kaizaki-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.07,0:16:50.48,Main Dialogue,Hishiro,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.86,0:16:52.74,Main Dialogue,Hishiro,0000,0000,0000,,You don't look good.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.57,0:16:55.16,Main Dialogue,Hishiro,0000,0000,0000,,Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.37,0:17:02.71,Main Dialogue,Hishiro,0000,0000,0000,,Kaizaki-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.66,0:17:04.92,Flashback Dialogue,Sempai,0000,0000,0000,,Kaizaki-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.13,0:17:14.63,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.59,0:17:16.76,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,If...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.26,0:17:19.26,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,...I'd only been more grown-up...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.26,0:17:22.89,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry. I'm sorry. I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.98,0:17:25.23,Main Dialogue,Hishiro,0000,0000,0000,,Kaizaki-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.85,0:17:29.57,Main Dialogue,Hishiro,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know why you're apologizing.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.11,0:17:36.91,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,Ow!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.57,0:17:40.62,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,S-Sorry, I didn't mean to do that!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.62,0:17:42.29,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,Don't call the police!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.29,0:17:44.75,Main Dialogue,Hishiro,0000,0000,0000,,I won't call the police.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.92,0:17:52.05,Main Dialogue,Hishiro,0000,0000,0000,,Good. You're back to normal.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.22,0:17:59.51,Italics Dialogue,Hishiro,0000,0000,0000,,About Kariu-san and Tamarai-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.51,0:18:02.47,Main Dialogue,Hishiro,0000,0000,0000,,Is it best that I do nothing?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.52,0:18:06.35,Main Dialogue,Hishiro,0000,0000,0000,,But I just don't like it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.35,0:18:08.22,Main Dialogue,Hishiro,0000,0000,0000,,They were so close.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.60,0:18:10.56,Main Dialogue,Hishiro,0000,0000,0000,,I don't like seeing them apart.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.23,0:18:13.61,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. I agree.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.61,0:18:16.15,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,It's hard to watch. I wanna do something.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.03,0:18:17.82,Italics Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.41,0:18:20.37,Italics Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,I'm scared.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.95,0:18:23.12,Italics Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,Scared of taking that step.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.12,0:18:25.45,Italics Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,What if I destroy everything again?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.16,0:18:28.87,Italics Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,I wasn't supposed to be their peer in school.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.87,0:18:31.79,Italics Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,I don't have the right to upset their lives.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.84,0:18:36.09,Main Dialogue,Hishiro,0000,0000,0000,,Then let's get revenge together.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.97,0:18:42.76,Main Dialogue,Hishiro,0000,0000,0000,,I want to defeat the me \Nthat's dragging this failure around.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.76,0:18:45.60,Main Dialogue,Hishiro,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want to forget my failure.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.35,0:18:51.27,Main Dialogue,Hishiro,0000,0000,0000,,But if I carry it with me as a bad memory, \Nand keep running away,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.27,0:18:53.61,Main Dialogue,Hishiro,0000,0000,0000,,I'll never change.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.98,0:18:58.36,Italics Dialogue,Hishiro,0000,0000,0000,,I think there are things \Nyou learn to do through failing.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.15,0:19:00.24,Main Dialogue,Hishiro,0000,0000,0000,,Kaizaki-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.74,0:19:06.70,Main Dialogue,Hishiro,0000,0000,0000,,Will you get revenge with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.96,0:19:13.67,Main Dialogue,Hishiro,0000,0000,0000,,Fight on!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.26,0:19:25.36,Main Dialogue,Team,0000,0000,0000,,Bye!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.39,0:19:28.10,Main Dialogue,Team,0000,0000,0000,,We're headed home. Are you good to clean up?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.10,0:19:31.40,Main Dialogue,Honoka,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yeah! Thanks! You go on home.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.40,0:19:32.31,Main Dialogue,Team,0000,0000,0000,,Bye!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.31,0:19:34.06,Main Dialogue,Team,0000,0000,0000,,Don't push yourself too hard!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.13,0:20:01.47,Main Dialogue,Honoka,0000,0000,0000,,Hishiron?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.47,0:20:02.84,Main Dialogue,Hishiro,0000,0000,0000,,Tamarai-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.84,0:20:04.68,Main Dialogue,Hishiro,0000,0000,0000,,Can we talk?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.22,0:20:10.02,Main Dialogue,Asaji,0000,0000,0000,,Tama-chan never showed up.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.02,0:20:11.73,Main Dialogue,Asaji,0000,0000,0000,,Think she went home already?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.73,0:20:14.77,Main Dialogue,Inukai,0000,0000,0000,,Without telling us? No way.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.52,0:20:19.61,Main Dialogue,Asaji,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? She's not here.\NDid she really go home?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.61,0:20:21.78,Main Dialogue,Inukai,0000,0000,0000,,And leave this mess behind?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.28,0:20:23.41,Main Dialogue,Asaji,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe she's in the clubroom?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.00,0:20:31.41,Main Dialogue,Hishiro,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.41,0:20:32.92,Main Dialogue,Hishiro,0000,0000,0000,,Kariu-san's sprain is...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.50,0:20:35.08,Main Dialogue,Honoka,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry, Hishiron.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.08,0:20:37.42,Main Dialogue,Hishiro,0000,0000,0000,,We're all eating separately.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.42,0:20:39.92,Main Dialogue,Hishiro,0000,0000,0000,,That's sort of beside the point.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.80,0:20:45.22,Main Dialogue,Honoka,0000,0000,0000,,I want to play this last tournament with her.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.22,0:20:47.51,Main Dialogue,Honoka,0000,0000,0000,,But I caused her injury,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.51,0:20:49.42,Main Dialogue,Honoka,0000,0000,0000,,so I don't know what to say.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.93,0:20:51.98,Main Dialogue,Honoka,0000,0000,0000,,I can't bring myself to talk to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.35,0:20:57.19,Main Dialogue,Asaji,0000,0000,0000,,Aki? Where are you going?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.90,0:21:00.73,Main Dialogue,Inukai,0000,0000,0000,,That redhead was still at school, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.19,0:21:03.15,Main Dialogue,Inukai,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna make her \Nlisten to how Tama feels.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.90,0:21:05.82,Main Dialogue,Inukai,0000,0000,0000,,I'm allowed to do that much, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.16,0:21:11.83,Main Dialogue,Rena,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, let go! What the hell?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.83,0:21:13.12,Main Dialogue,Oga,0000,0000,0000,,Inukai-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.12,0:21:14.87,Main Dialogue,Oga,0000,0000,0000,,You're hurting her!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.87,0:21:17.21,Main Dialogue,Oga,0000,0000,0000,,Inukai-kun! Listen!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.21,0:21:20.55,Italics Dialogue,Rena,0000,0000,0000,,This guy! He's taking me to Honoka...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.42,0:21:22.76,Main Dialogue,Rena,0000,0000,0000,,Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.76,0:21:24.76,Main Dialogue,Inukai,0000,0000,0000,,From here on, keep it down.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.76,0:21:26.76,Main Dialogue,Inukai,0000,0000,0000,,Even your footsteps.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.76,0:21:28.51,Main Dialogue,Inukai,0000,0000,0000,,If you must talk, whisper.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.97,0:21:32.02,Main Dialogue,Oga,0000,0000,0000,,Okay. We'll do what you say.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.03,0:21:48.66,Main Dialogue,Inukai,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up and listen.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.62,0:21:52.49,Main Dialogue,Honoka,0000,0000,0000,,The truth is...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.66,0:21:54.79,Main Dialogue,Honoka,0000,0000,0000,,Honestly,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.00,0:22:00.90,Main Dialogue,Honoka,0000,0000,0000,,I wasn't going to play volleyball \Nin high school.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.96,0:23:39.97,Next Episode,,0000,0000,0000,,NEXT EPISODE
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.84,0:23:28.29,Main Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hishiro-san, what was that\N "fight on" thing all about?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.29,0:23:31.55,Main Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I learned about it when\NI studied up on sports teams.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.55,0:23:34.29,Main Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a teamwork ritual where\Neveryone joins hands and...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.29,0:23:34.89,Main Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.89,0:23:36.40,Main Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Join me, if you like.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.06,0:23:39.97,Next Episode Title,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1200,1)}Everyone's Selfish Desires
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.62,0:23:38.02,Main Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Fight on!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.38,0:23:39.52,Main Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,On... Oh.
